    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hi everyone! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, and it runs like a dream! Whether you\u2019re heading to work or taking a weekend trip, this car is totally ready for its next adventure. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Come take it for a spin!",
