    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_23_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_23",
      "description": "This 2016 Lexus RC 350 F Sport in Nebula Gray Pearl is a stunning example of the balance between luxury and performance. The exterior maintains a deep, mirror-like shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the Rioja Red leather seats remain supple and supportive, with only light bolstering wear on the driver\u2019s side. Every feature, from the Mark Levinson premium audio to the heated and ventilated seats, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle has been meticulously cared for, featuring a fully documented service history, a recent set of Michelin Pilot Sport tires, and a fresh brake service performed within the last 2,000 miles. It drives straight and true, with the 3.5L V6 delivering smooth, responsive power through every gear. It is a turn-key grand tourer that has been smoke-free and garage-kept, ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 33500.0,
